      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.7gsxV0nk1qel9Xow]{Devastator}</p>\n<p>When you score a critical hit with an attack, you can spend 1 Resolve Point as a swift action to add the wound critical hit effect to the attack, replacing any other critical hit effect the attack has. If the attack would already have the wound critical hit effect, you can instead spend 1 Resolve Point to add the severe wound critical hit effect to the attack in place of other critical hit effects.</p>"
